<P><BASE href="http://www.justpeace.org/mixes.htm">
<SPAN STYLE="font-size: 24pt" STYLE="COLOR: #006600"><STRONG>MAKE YOUR OWN MIXES!</STRONG></SPAN></P>

<P>Why pay high prices for expensive store mixes when you can make your own and thus control the quality, protect the nutrition, and serve tasty foods that don't
cost much money?  Not to mention, they are time-savers.  This page has recipes for various common mixes that you can do<A NAME="for yourself."> for yourself.</A>  </P>

<P><SPAN STYLE="font-family: Arial" STYLE="font-size: 10pt"><STRONG><A HREF="http://www.justpeace.org/better.htm">Better Times II</A></STRONG></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-family: Arial" STYLE="font-size: 10pt"><STRONG>| <A HREF="http://www.justpeace.org/">Justpeace</A> |  <A HREF="http://www.bettertimesinfo.org">Better Times</A> | <A HREF="http://www.bobwaldrop.net">BobWaldrop.net</A> |<A HREF="http://www.energyconservationinfo.org">Access to Energy Conservation</A> | <A HREF="http://www.onpilgrimage.justpeace.org">On Pilgrimage in Oklahoma City</A> | <A HREF="http://www.justpeace.org/bookindex.htm">Bookstore</A> | <A HREF="http://www.bettertimesinfo.org/2004index.htm">Better Times
Cookbook V</A> </STRONG></SPAN></P>

